HEADWORD: Ladys comb
<hw>La"dy's comb"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>An
umbelliferous plant (<spn>Scandix Pecten-Veneris</spn>), its clusters of
long slender fruits remotely resembling a comb.</def>⟦br⟧
